<collectionCode id="ED63AE45321C9807FBB411BBFB66FF0D" box="[1131,1242,188,212]" pageId="23" pageNumber="80">MNHUB</collectionCode>
). The number on the blue handwritten label corresponds to the data: “53946 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D03321C9807FCEF11D8FC72FF21" authority="Suffr." authorityName="Suffrian" authorityYear="1866" box="[816,974,223,248]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metallactus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="80" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="spilotus">spilotus Suffr.</taxonomicName>
